**Version**: 2.4  
**Last Updated**: 2025-12-23  
**Status**: Official Standard  
**Applies To**: All xTalent Modules

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **v2.4 Major Update - One Entity Per File**: Ontology entities are now documented in separate files (one entity = one file) within sub-module folders for better maintainability and AI agent efficiency. See Templates 1A-NEW and 1B-NEW.

